Two motorbike drivers died in a head-on collision on the R704 outside Bloemfontein on Saturday.It is believed that both drivers are in their 40&#8217;s.ER24 Spokesperson Annine Dormehl said paramedics were first to arrive at the scene at 2pm, where they found both motorbikes burning.The road was closed for cleaning and local authorities were investigating the accident.-TNA Reporter